    ? "Move ←/→/↑/↓  •  Rotate l/L  •  Scale i/I  •  Undo k  •  Redo K  •  Enter OK  •  J = Menu  •  j = Select Object"
    : "Choose IMAGE  •  ←/→ to pick  •  Enter to SELECT  •  ↑ back to catalogs  •  J = Menu  •  Undo k  •  Redo K";
